{"lastModified":1761149283795,"uri":"c::7819281976::vessel::986fb160-34bf-11f0-bfb5-e754accc3a56","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Amalfi Coast, Capri, Destinations, Ischia, Italy, Naples, Palmarola, Pontine Islands, Ponza, Positano, Procida, Sorrento, Ventotene\n\nMAGISTRA, an Apreamare yacht, crafted in Sorrento by the Apreamare shipyard, Italy stands for quality, tradition and design integrity. Renowned as the ‘Bentley of the sea’, sophisticated and spacious, combining old traditional style into a modern design classic. Reliable, comfortable, but especially agile and fast. Elegant deck lines of the Apreamare 60, with the large size of the side walkway, allow you to move around with great ease. The large sundeck and sofas provide spacious areas to relax and sunbathe. The epitome of high-end Italian yachts for those who wish to charter with relaxed elegance and style. It is the perfect mode of choice to enjoy the splendor of the Amalfi Coast and surrounding islands.\n\nMAGISTRA Apreamare 60 motor yacht of the “Gozzo” range with 3 cabins built in 2007 by Cantieri Apreamare and refitted in 2024. Experience luxury and style on the high seas with this yacht crafted with Italian precision and renowned for its timeless design. Magistra offers a perfect blend of performance, comfort and refinement.\nThe yacht has the charm of the Mediterranean style and authentic made in Italy. A refined design, capable of combining tradition and innovation.\n\nMagistra is based in Marina di Stabia, near Salerno, for charters on the Amalfi Coast, Capri, Ischia, Pontines Islands and other nearby areas upon request and booking availability.\n\nGuest accommodation: Magistra accommodates 6 people in three ensuite cabins. Max guests on board 12 (daily).","blueprint":{"name":"MAGISTRA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::986fb160-34bf-11f0-bfb5-e754accc3a56::assets::8b0f1060-34c4-11f0-a6a5-bf4e7abe5a75/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::986fb160-34bf-11f